OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat the Bristol Royal Infirmary (BRI)
OL,8,Fand people are being asked not to
OL,9,Fattend the hospital.
OL,11,FUniversity Hospitals Bristol and
OL,12,FWeston NHS Foundation Trust said "a
OL,13,Fpower outage" is affecting its
OL,14,Fhospitals in Bristol city centre.
OL,16,FThe Trust runs multiple sites in the
OL,17,Fcentre of the city including the BRI,
OL,18,FBristol Royal Hospital for Children,
OL,19,FSt Michael's Hospital and Bristol Eye
OL,20,FHospital.
