OL,3,CPeople asked not to go to Bristol
OL,4,Chospital as critical incident declared
OL,6,FIn a statement, interim chief medical
OL,7,Fofficer at UHBW Dr Rebecca Maxwell
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have declared a critical
OL,9,Fincident due to a power outage. We aim
OL,10,Fto have this fully resolved as soon as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,F"I would like to share with the public
OL,14,Fthat every single patient, visitor and
OL,15,Fcolleagues are safe.
OL,17,F"Our adult emergency department is
OL,18,Fcurrently closed to patients but the
OL,19,Fchildren's emergency department is
OL,20,Fopen.
