OL,3,CPeople asked not to go to Bristol
OL,4,Chospital as critical incident declared
OL,6,F"We ask the public not to attend our
OL,7,FBristol city centre hospitals until
OL,8,Fthe incident is resolved and use
OL,9,Falternative services in the area.
OL,11,F"We have an emergency power back-up
OL,12,Fgenerator that is supplying a lot of
OL,13,Fpower to the hospital and we're
OL,14,Fbringing more generators in to support
OL,15,Fthat.
OL,17,F"One or two areas in the hospital do
OL,18,Fnot have lights at the moment and one
OL,19,Fof those is part of the adult
OL,20,Femergency department which is closed
OL,21,Fto new patients."
