OL,6,FAt 9:18pm Dr Rebecca Maxwell said:
OL,7,F"Our adult Emergency Department is now
OL,8,Fopen to urgent walk-in patients. Our
OL,9,FChildren's Emergency Department
OL,10,Fremains open to both ambulances and
OL,11,Fwalk-in patients.
OL,13,F"If you have a life threatening
OL,14,Femergency please dial 999, for any
OL,15,Fother urgent medical advice please use
OL,16,F.
